<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīśākē ratnarāmā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nilaśaśigaṇitē caitramāsē vaḷakṣē
<lb n="3"/>pakṣēṣṭamyāṁ sitā<unclear>hē</unclear> kharakarasahi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tē dharmaliṁgasya mēṣē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Anyāṁbā
<lb n="5"/>paṁcadhārāpurakṛtavasatērdīpa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mā caṁdratāraṁ dēvī prādādakhaṁḍaṁ
<lb n="7"/>phaladamanudinaṁ nāgabhūmīśvarasya [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
<lb n="8"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1339 gu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nēṁṭi hēmalaṁbi saṁvatsara caitra śu
<lb n="10"/>8 śu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> mēṣasaṁkrāṁti puṇyakālamaṁ
<lb n="11" break="no"/>du śrīviṣṇuvardhanamahārājulai
<lb n="12" break="no"/>na nāgēṁdradēvacakravarttula dēviyai
<lb n="13" break="no"/>na Anyamadēvi tanaku ciṁttitamanō
<lb n="14" break="no"/>rathasiddhigānunnu saṁttānābhivṛddhigānu
<lb n="15" break="no"/>nnu paṁcadhārala dharmēśvaraliṁgāna
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ku pratidinamunnu mānadī pānakai go
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṛṟelu 50 nnivelavuḷlalōnu polamu
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ṁ dharmēśvaraliṁgānaku maḍuva
<lb n="19" break="no"/>liki na 5 [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>] Ī dīpamu naḍapi<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>pi sō
<lb n="20" break="no"/>mula gaṁganabōyini koḍuku
<lb n="21" break="no"/>lu sūrebōṁḍinni kūnabōṁḍinni mā
<lb n="22" break="no"/>ṁkana bōṁḍinni vīrikini ve<unclear>dapa</unclear>ru būmi
<lb n="23"/>Uttarānanu vaṁdumu kṣētra
<lb n="24" break="no"/>mu Ācaṁdrārkamugā niccenu [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
</p>

